metadata.name: Breath
metadata.description:
The name of this photo is 'Breathe'

This photo is a street portrait of an old man living in Turkey.

I photographed the man who had to go to hospitals in different cities due to his illness, while he was smoking a cigarette in front of his daughter's house. I left him saying that smoking is harmful to health.
